<html><head></head><body><div class="docs-markdown"><p class="docs-markdown-p">Mosaic cards are controls to display statuses/states/messages.</p><div mosaic-docs-example="card-overview"></div><h3 id="properties" class="docs-header-link docs-markdown-h3"><span header-link="properties"></span> Properties</h3><p class="docs-markdown-p">There are four properties to interact with control:</p><table class="docs-markdown-table"><thead><tr class="docs-markdown-tr"><th class="docs-markdown-th">Property</th><th class="docs-markdown-th">Description</th></tr></thead><tbody class="docs-markdown-tbody"><tr class="docs-markdown-tr"><td class="docs-markdown-td"><code class="docs-markdown-code">[status]</code></td><td class="docs-markdown-td">Enum value Status(Info, Success, Warning, Error). Default value is Status.Info. It set color visual state of control.</td></tr><tr class="docs-markdown-tr"><td class="docs-markdown-td"><code class="docs-markdown-code">[mode]</code></td><td class="docs-markdown-td">There are two values 'color' and 'white'. This affects how the background is displayed. Default value is 'color'</td></tr><tr class="docs-markdown-tr"><td class="docs-markdown-td"><code class="docs-markdown-code">[readonly]</code></td><td class="docs-markdown-td">When set to 'true' control is switched to not interactive mode. It can't be focused or selected</td></tr><tr class="docs-markdown-tr"><td class="docs-markdown-td"><code class="docs-markdown-code">[selected]</code></td><td class="docs-markdown-td">It switch control to the selected visual state.</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="events" class="docs-header-link docs-markdown-h3"><span header-link="events"></span> Events</h3><p class="docs-markdown-p">There is one output event:</p><table class="docs-markdown-table"><thead><tr class="docs-markdown-tr"><th class="docs-markdown-th">Event</th><th class="docs-markdown-th">Description</th></tr></thead><tbody class="docs-markdown-tbody"><tr class="docs-markdown-tr"><td class="docs-markdown-td"><code class="docs-markdown-code">(selectedChange)</code></td><td class="docs-markdown-td">It happens when user click on control and and [readonly] set to 'false'</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="content" class="docs-header-link docs-markdown-h3"><span header-link="content"></span> Content</h3><p class="docs-markdown-p">It is possible to add additional content on the left and on the right side from main content by using attributes 'content-left' and 'content-right'.</p><h3 id="theming" class="docs-header-link docs-markdown-h3"><span header-link="theming"></span> Theming</h3><h3 id="accessibility" class="docs-header-link docs-markdown-h3"><span header-link="accessibility"></span> Accessibility</h3></div></body></html>